# 中文：仓库忽略规则，避免提交缓存、虚拟环境和生成的模型/报告产物。
# English: Repository ignore rules for caches, virtual environments, and generated model/report artifacts.

__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.venv/
artifacts/**/*.json
artifacts/**/*.jsonl
artifacts/**/*.md
artifacts/**/*.onnx
artifacts/**/*.pt
artifacts/**/*.pth
artifacts/**/*.png
artifacts/**/*.pdf
